# AI-Driven Data Analytics Dashboard — "DataMind"

Build a premium, visually stunning AI-powered data analytics web application that lets users upload datasets, explore data with AI-generated insights, query data using natural language, visualize trends with auto-generated charts, and clean/export datasets — all from a single beautiful interface.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **AI Backend**: This plan uses a **client-side AI engine** (statistical analysis + heuristics) for insights, pattern detection, and natural language queries — no API key needed. The architecture supports easy swap to OpenAI/Gemini APIs if desired later.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Tech Stack**: Pure HTML/CSS/JavaScript (no frameworks). Libraries loaded via CDN: Chart.js (charts), Papa Parse (CSV), SheetJS (Excel). This keeps the app lightweight and zero-install.

