## Feature Breakdown

### 1. 🏠 Landing & Upload Zone
- Stunning dark-mode hero section with animated gradient background
- Drag-and-drop file upload with animated dropzone
- Support for **CSV**, **JSON**, and **Excel** (.xlsx) files
- File validation, size checks, and progress indicator
- Sample datasets to try instantly (pre-loaded demo data)

### 2. 📋 Data Explorer
- Interactive data table with sorting, filtering, and pagination
- Column statistics panel (type, min/max, mean, unique count, null count)
- Data type auto-detection (numeric, categorical, date, boolean)
- Search across all columns
- Row count and memory usage indicators

### 3. 🤖 AI Insights Engine (Client-Side)
- **Auto-generated insights** on data load:
  - Statistical summaries per column
  - Correlation detection between numeric columns
  - Outlier detection (IQR method)
  - Missing data patterns
  - Distribution analysis (normal, skewed, uniform)
  - Trend detection for time-series data
- **Insight cards** with severity ratings (info, warning, critical)
- Each insight includes a recommended action

### 4. 💬 Natural Language Query Chat
- Chat interface to ask questions about the dataset
- Built-in NLP parser handles queries like:
  - *"What is the average salary?"*
  - *"Show top 10 rows by revenue"*
  - *"How many missing values are there?"*
  - *"What columns are correlated?"*
  - *"Show distribution of age"*
- Responses include data tables, charts, and text explanations
- Query history and suggested questions

### 5. 📈 Visualization Dashboard
- **Auto-suggested charts** based on data types
- Chart types: Bar, Line, Pie, Doughnut, Scatter, Histogram, Radar
- Interactive chart builder — pick X/Y axes, grouping, aggregation
- Real-time chart preview with smooth animations
- Export charts as PNG images
- Responsive chart grid layout

### 6. 🧹 Data Cleaning Studio
- AI-detected issues panel:
  - Missing values (with fill strategies: mean, median, mode, drop)
  - Duplicate rows detection and removal
  - Outlier flagging
  - Data type inconsistencies
- One-click fix buttons for each issue
- Before/after comparison view
- Undo/redo support
- Export cleaned dataset as CSV or JSON

